parameters:
\nc<>Congratulations, Senpai! It's a great achievement! The
number of visitors has skyrocketed all at once, right?!

\nc<>The popularity has also increased significantly, and above
all, because it's for helping people, there are no
haters...!
\nc<>Ah, what have I done...! I'm sorry, Matsuo-san!
\nc<>I don't think you need to worry about it, you know?

\nc<>Certainly, the livestream on that day was ruined, but it
should be a plus in the future because it became a topic of
conversation.
\nc<>Well, if you really feel sorry, Senpai.

\nc<>How about accepting the offer for a collaboration on a
drinking livestream that just came from over there?

\nc<>A drinking livestream, huh... I'm not really good with
alcohol though...

\nc<>(I should have definitely refused as usual...) (But the fact
is, I broke my promise.)
\nc<>Hehe. Take your time and think carefully before deciding.

\nc<>Good listeners increased by 7,000, while bad listeners
increased by 3,000.
